@DATABASE "Midnight Resistance 48K"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - M - Midnight Resistance 48K"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - M
                   ====================================

                          Midnight Resistance 48K
                          =======================



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" rxs "address command zxampoke(36480,0)"}          36480,0
@{"Lives = x     " rxs "address command zxampoke(31760,255)"}          31760,x (x= 1- 255)
@{"Infinite Weapons" rxs "address command zxampoke(39975,0)"}        39975,0
@{"Infinite Backpacks" rxs "address command zxampoke(39996,0)"}      39996,0


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         Note the "Infinite Weapons" POKE only
                         works once you HAVE the weapons.

                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
